    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in good condition, and prospective buyers will find it to be a reliable and well-maintained option. The exterior shows only minor signs of normal wear \u2014 small surface scratches and light paint fade in a couple of areas \u2014 but overall presents quite well with no dents or significant blemishes. The interior is clean and functional, with moderate wear on the seats and some light scuffing on high-contact surfaces like the door panels and center console, all consistent with regular use. Mechanically, the car runs well \u2014 the engine starts reliably, transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems including brakes, suspension, and HVAC are in proper working order. There are no known major mechanical issues, though as with any used vehicle, routine maintenance items may come due. This is a solid, honest everyday driver that has been cared for but is not without the typical signs of age and use.",
